{"tid":790051,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[執柒左佢] 《TVB周刊》由網版取代","createTime":"2018-08-22T16:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T00:02:20.000Z","uid":167658,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f9c474e94451fcb0c10b69cfe418eec786555155","tid":790051,"uid":167658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T16:39:24.000Z","msg":"電視廣播(TVB，511)公佈，半年純利為2.01億元，同比升18%，每股盈利0.46元，中期息維持0.3元。惟計算匯兌差異及一家聯營公司其他全面收益後，全面收益總額為2.12億元，同比跌12%。<br />\n<br />\n分部業績方面，包括大台網及星夢娛樂所產生的外部客戶收入總額為2700萬元。自大台網所產生的廣告收入不斷上升。但由於前期資本及營運投資，有關分部於期內錄得分部虧損2000萬元。<br />\n<br />\n來自廣告客戶的收入於期內同比升2%至11.51億元，按年計，其中開支最高五大類別為奶粉（跌3%）、貸款及按揭（升5%）、旅行社（升14%）、藥物及保健品（升27%）及個人護膚品（升15%）。期內收入增幅最大者為一般銀行類（升90%）。而來自地產（下跌64%）及政府（下跌27%）的開支下跌，抵銷收入增幅。<br />\n<br />\n[size=4]<span style=\"color: red;\">另外，公司提到雜誌的印刷本將由網上版取代，所指應該是《TVB周刊》。[/</span>size=4]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本野真係仲有人買架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0fcfb71c97b3ff451275910b4c6e7216e43504","tid":790051,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T16:43:33.000Z","msg":"咩人會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6fbe9c1406ddb8f2e2dd09b83e17c5c1db26fe9","tid":790051,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:16:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b4e23e36ecef0c6c3457b4375db6b5505d1588a","tid":790051,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T23:57:33.000Z","msg":"以前為個file買過本<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"h